reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect addition to counter
reviews.reviewText: I really enjoy this little turtle. It came packed extremely well so I wouldn't worry about breakage. The colors are better than pictured and is a perfect match to the rest of my blue coastal themed counter. The base and dowel holding paper is nice wood tone but not as heavy and strong as I thought it would be. It is my favorite accessory on my counter .It serves it's purpose just fine just don't go ripping any towels from holder without holding on to it. This little guy should, hopefully, last years as I really like him.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been waiting for it to go on sale, but, don’t wait!! It is adorable, sturdy & even better than the online picture!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Was delivered quickly & is exactly as described by seller BEAUTIFUL & exactly what I was looking for to use at a beach houseCame very well packaged so no damage to the adorable turtle & easy to assemble Worth the money for the uniqueness & quality of the product

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute beachy themed paper towel holder
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this for the esthetic of the turtle to be honest. So it was definitely a splurge because I could have gotten another less expensive yet highly functional paper towel holder but that's not what I was going for.My kitchen and living room are beach themed, and I have turtle sticker decals on my walls. So, this paper towel holder definitely matches my existing décor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sea Turtle Paper Towel Holder
reviews.reviewText: This fun paper towel holder looks adorable on my new countertop in my remodeled kitchen! Love the color and the sea turtle is a perfect accent in my island home! Thank you, Karen Anderson

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Turtle is nice, the wood could be upgraded, the MAIN ISSUE is the turtle is close in so you can only use single size paper towels which actually is hard to find, jumbo sized like double or triples won’t fit and that size is now standard in grocery stores. They need to make the base wider.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not for big rolls
reviews.reviewText: Love the design and quality but I guess I didn’t read into verifying if it’s meant to hold large rolls of paper towels because it doesn’t…at least with the turtle on so I had to leave it off for it to actually be useful. So while it’s a quality product, I’m not giving this a 5-star because it doesn’t hold all sizes of paper towels. Bummer cause I really like the turtle too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
